### 3. Draft Addendum (Formal)

**ADDENDUM TO MASTER SERVICE AGREEMENT (MSA) DATED [DATE]**

This Addendum is entered into by and between Cognizant Technology Solutions India Pvt. Ltd. ("Cognizant") and [Vendor Name] ("Vendor").

**1. ADVANCE PAYMENT:** Cognizant agrees to pay an advance of INR [Amount] as a one-time payment. This payment is subject to the Vendor providing a valid Proforma Invoice.

**2. PERFORMANCE OBLIGATION:** The Vendor acknowledges that this advance is strictly for the delivery of [Project Name/Service]. The Vendor represents that they are capable of fulfilling the delivery obligations as per the SOW.

**3. LIABILITY & RECOVERY:** 
(a) Pursuant to **Section 39 of the Indian Contract Act, 1872**, if the Vendor fails to perform their obligations, Cognizant shall be entitled to terminate the contract and demand a full refund of the advance payment within 7 days of notice.
(b) The Vendor acknowledges that failure to deliver constitutes a material breach, and the advance amount shall be treated as a debt due to Cognizant, recoverable under the provisions of the **Code of Civil Procedure, 1908**.

